%20debated%20and%20criticised%20Ram%20Madhav%20and%20the%20RSS%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Yes%2C%20of%20course%20I%20have%E2%80%99.%20You%20know%2C%20I%20have%20been%20on%20that%20TV%20debate%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20public%20and%20that%20was%20in%202015%2C%20and%20I%20did%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98That%20was%20nine%20years%20ago%2C%20what%20has%20that%20got%20to%20do%20with%20anything%20now%3F%E2%80%99%20They%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20testimony%20then%2C%20but%20they%20did%20mention%20Ram%20Madhav%20and%20the%20RSS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20informal%2C%20it%20was%20not%20%E2%80%A6%20when%20I%20asked%20them%20for%20a%20reason%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20that%2C%20but%20they%20did%20ask%20me%20that.%20And%20it%20was%20the%20only%20thing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20firstly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20bizarre%20that%20they%20would%20give%20reasons%20to%20newspapers%20and%20TV%20channels%20and%20not%2C%20you%20know%2C%20which%20are%20also%20very%20specious%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20patchwork%20of%20%E2%80%A6%20a%20quilt%20of%20unsubstantiated%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20regarding%20the%20use%20of%20terminology%2C%20well%2C%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20talking%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20context%2C%20obviously%20historically%2C%20one%20would%20speak%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20now%20the%20Union%20territories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20talking%20in%20the%20context%20of%20international%20relations%2C%20that%20is%20the%20standard%2C%20normal%2C%20legal%20terminology%20of%20using%20administration.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20neutral%20term%2C%20it%20does%20not%20reflect%20in%20any%20way%20on%20any%20claims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20simply%20drawing%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20ther