t%20call%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20tourism.%20Mr%20Nasheed%2C%20currently%20in%20India%2C%20also%20issued%20an%20apology%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diplomatic%20strain%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives%2C%20simmering%20for%20a%20while%2C%20hit%20another%20low%20as%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%2C%20perceived%20as%20pro-China%2C%20announced%20plans%20to%20expel%20all%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20from%20the%20country%20by%20March%2010.%20This%20move%20raised%20tensions%20and%20prompted%20a%20boycott%20call%20from%20India%2C%20impacting%20various%20sectors%2C%20notably%20tourism%2C%20a%20crucial%20component%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20impacted%20the%20Maldives%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20I%20am%20actually%20here%20in%20India.%20I'm%20very%20worried%20about%20this.%20I%20want%20to%20say%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Maldives%20are%20sorry%2C%20we%20are%20sorry%20that%20this%20has%20happened.%20We%20want%20Indian%20people%20to%20come%20on%20their%20holidays%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20and%20there%20will%20not%20be%20any%20change%20in%20our%20hospitality%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nasheed%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nasheed%20acknowledged%20India's%20historically%20responsible%20approach%20in%20dealing%20with%20such%20matters%2C%20stating%20that%20instead%20of%20exerting%20pressure%2C%20India%20proposed%20a%20diplomatic%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Maldives%20wanted%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20to%20leave%2C%20you%20know%20what%20India%20did%3F%20They%20did%20not%20twist%20their%20arms.%20They%20did%20not%20display%20muscle%2C%20but%20just%20simply%20told%20the%20government%20of%20Maldives%2C%20'Okay%2C%20let's%20have%20a%20discussion%20on%20that'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20recent%20defence%20agreement%20between%20Maldives%20and%20China%2C%20Mr%20Nasheed%20dismissed%20it%20as%20not%20being%20a%20defence%20pact%20but%20rather%20an%20acquisition%20of%20equipment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20Muizzu%20wanted%20to%20buy%20some%20equipment%2C%20mainly%20rubber%20bullets%20and%20tear%20gas.%20It%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20government%20thought%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20more%20tear%20gas%20and%20more%20rubber%20bullets.%20Governance%20is%20not%20through%20the%20barrel%20of%20the%20gun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20recently%20stated%20that%20misunderstandings%20can%20arise%20between%20nations%20and%20expressed%20optimism%20in%20resolving%20the%20dispute%20through%20diplomatic%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHumanity%20is%20humanity.%20Diplomacy%20is%20diplomacy%2C%20and%20politics%20is%20politics.%20The%20whole%20world%20doesn't%20always%20run%20with%20obligation...so%20if%20we%20have%20encountered%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20the%20solution%20will%20come%20through%20diplomacy%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20make%20people%20understand%2C%20sometimes%20people%20don't%20even%20have%20complete%20knowledge%20of%20things%2C%20sometimes%20people%20get%20misguided%20on%20what%20others%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Maldives%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20not%20extend%20the%20agreement%20that%20permitted%20India%20to%20conduct%20hydrographic%20surveys%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Muizzu%20broke%20from%20the%20established%20tradition%20by%20opting%20not%20to%20visit%20India%20on%20his%20first%20official%20trip%2C%20instead%20choosing%20to%20visit%20Turkey%20and%20then%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709949360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F3v45k9bo_mohamed-nasheed-afp_625x300_07_Apri