o-CEO%20Bret%20Taylor%20and%20former%20US%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Larry%20Summers%2C%20who%20joined%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20November%202023%20tumult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20also%20gained%20an%20observer%20seat%20on%20OpenAI's%20board%20at%20the%20time%2C%20a%20move%20that%20drew%20criticism%20and%20a%20lawsuit%20from%20Elon%20Musk%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20who%20helped%20found%20OpenAI%20in%202015%20before%20leaving%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20excited%20to%20welcome%20Sue%2C%20Nicole%2C%20and%20Fidji%20to%20the%20OpenAI%20Board%20of%20Directors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%C2%A0%20Bret%20Taylor%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20OpenAI%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20experience%20and%20leadership%20will...%20ensure%20that%20we%20pursue%20OpenAI's%20mission%20of%20ensuring%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20benefits%20all%20of%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuora%20CEO%20Adam%20D'Angelo%20is%20the%20sole%20holdover%20from%20the%20old%20board%20that%20had%20taken%20the%20decision%20to%20fire%20Altman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAltman%20has%20become%20the%20face%20of%20the%20recent%20artificial%20intelligence%20explosion%20that%20burst%20onto%20the%20scene%20with%20his%20decision%20to%20release%20ChatGPT%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20shock%20move%2C%20the%20company's%20board%20summarily%20fired%20Altman%20without%20any%20clear%20reason%20given%2C%20sparking%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20mass%20exodus%20by%20the%20company's%20700%20strong%20employees%2C%20who%20stuck%20by%20their%20star%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20with%20major%20investments%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20offered%20to%20hire%20those%20leaving%20the%20AI%20company%2C%20forcing%20a%20change%20of%20mind%20by%20its%20board%2C%20which%20reinstated%20Altman%20after%20a%20few%20days%20of%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20members%20behind%20Altman's%20shortlived%20ouster%2C%20left%20their%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Right%20leaders'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20events%2C%20the%20new%20fangled%20board%20launched%20an%20internal%20investigation%20on%20what%20happened%20with%20a%20law%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20that%20investigation%20%26quot%3Bunanimously%20concluded%20that%20Altman%20and%20president%20Greg%20Brockman%20%26quot%3Bare%20the%20right%20leaders%20for%20OpenAI%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said%20in%20a%20sperate%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20the%20probe%2C%20handled%20by%20outside%20firm%20WilmerHale%2C%20%26quot%3Breviewed%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20documents%3B%20conducted%20dozens%20of%20interviews%2C%20including%20of%20members%20of%20OpenAI's%20prior%20Board%2C%20OpenAI%20executives%2C%20advisors%20to%20the%20prior%20Board%2C%20and%20other%20pertinent%20witnesses...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20remains%20the%20standard%20bearer%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20the%20technology%20that%20can%20generate%20human%20level%20texts%20and%20images%20in%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20faces%20increased%20rivalry%20from%20Google%2C%20Meta%20and%20other%20startups%2C%20including%20Anthropic%2C%20Musk's%20xAI%20and%20French%20company%20Mistral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20now%20caught%20up%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20Musk%2C%20who%20accuses%20Altman%20and%20top%20executives%20of%20betraying%20the%20original%20nonprofit%20status%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20suit%20alleges%20that%20OpenAI%20was%20now%20effectively%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Microsoft%2C%20arguing%20that%20this%20was%20breach%20of%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20embrace%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20OpenAI's%20technology%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20made%20it%20the%20world's%20biggest%20company%20by%20market%20capitalization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20also%20being%20sued%20by%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20for%20allegedly%20illegally%2