0that%20the%20casting%20of%20a%20vote%20of%20credible%20value%20by%20the%20citizen%20is%20intimately%20related%20to%20her%20knowledge%20of%20the%20funding%20of%20the%20political%20protagonists%20vying%20for%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20minced%20no%20words%20in%20laying%20down%20that%20the%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20information%20in%20this%20matter%2C%20more%20than%20most%2C%C2%A0%20is%20a%20sine%20qua%20non%20of%20a%20trustworthy%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20happily%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Feditorials%2Fexpress-view-on-sbis-delay-in-electoral-bonds-disclosure-do-it-before-the-election-9199816%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Feditorials%2Fexpress-view-on-sbis-delay-in-electoral-bonds-disclosure-do-it-before-the-election-9199816%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709993946624000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw24sqCywgr_pFNAaBjO_O3b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20otherwise%20corporate-friendly%20leading%20daily%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20put%20the%20matter%20succinctly%2C%20and%20without%20hemming%20and%20hawing%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20most%20%E2%80%9Cmainstream%E2%80%9D%20media%20outlets%20seem%20too%20%E2%80%9Ccabined%2C%20cribbed%2C%20and%20confined%E2%80%9D%20(borrowing%20from%20Macbeth)%20to%20come%20out%20with%20courage%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20democratic%20right%20and%20proper%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20top%20court%20had%20stipulated%20certain%20dates%20for%20the%20SBI%20to%20make%20the%20requisite%20disclosures%20of%20bonds%20bought%20and%20donated%2C%20it%20was%20clearly%20with%20a%20view%20to%20furnishing%20such%20information%20to%20the%20citizen%20in%20a%20given%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20idea%20has%20to%20have%20been%20to%20enable%20the%20disclosures%20before%20a%20code%20of%20conduct%20set%20in%20following%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20to%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20malingering%20fools%20nobody%2C%20in%20that%20the%20date%20of%20disclosure%20demanded%20by%20it%2C%20namely%2C%20June%2030%2C%20is%20cannily%20chosen%3B%20by%20then%20the%20said%20elections%C2%A0will%20be%20done%20and%20dusted%2C%20with%20nobody%20any%20the%20wiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20much%20the%20bank%20may%20plead%20that%20no%20such%20motive%20attaches%20to%20its%20modus%20operandi%2C%20free-thinking%20and%20fair-minded%20citizens%20know%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20editorially%20remarked%2C%20citizens%20who%20seek%20a%20republic%20that%20results%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20and%20fair%E2%80%9D%20exercise%20of%20choice%2C%20need%20to%20have%20the%20information%20hidden%20away%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20order%20to%20make%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20and%20fair%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20determination%2C%20one%20way%20or%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20citizens%20will%20thus%20look%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20yet%20again%20to%20put%20its%20constitutional%20foot%20down%20with%20firm%20conviction%20when%20the%20appeal%20for%20delaying%20disclosure%20comes%20up%20before%20it%20on%20March%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20most%20experts%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20banking%20practices%20have%20averred%20that%20compliance%20with%20the%20limited%20directions%20of%20the%20top%20court%20should%20not%20take%20more%20than%20a%20day%20in%20this%20digital%20time%2C%20surely%20the%C2%A0%20SBI%20will%20need%20to%20explain%20the%20rationale%20behind%20its%20suspiciously%20laggard%20gambit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20indeed%20has%20a%20good%20case%2C%20it%20must%20seize%20the%20opportunity%20to%20vindicate%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20that%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20legislation%20requires%20that%20bonds%20not%20cashed%20must%20be%20deposited%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CPM%20Cares%E2%80%9D%20Fund%20within%2015%20days.%20Pray%2C%20how%20can%20the%20bank%20ever%20do%20this%20unless%20they%20are%20already%20in%20command%20of%20all%20the%20information%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20such%20a%20stipulation%20at%20all%20exists%20within%20the%20bonds%20rules%20may%20of%20course%20be%20the%20subject%20of%20another%20curiosity%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20recall%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CPM%20Cares%20Fund%E2%80%9D%20has%20often%20taken%20a%20dual%20stance%20in%20the%20matter%20of%2C%20one%2C%20the%20citizen%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20right%20to%20information%20about%20its%20doings%2C%20and%20then%20about%20its%20power%20to%20obtain%20donations%20from%20public%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20has%20been%20demanded%20that%20this%20fund%20also%20be%20amenable%20to%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Law%2C%20the%20Fund%20has%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprivate%E2%80%9D%20entity%2C%20and%20thus%C2%A0%20not%20obliged%20to%20make%20disclosures%20to%20the%20public%3B%20but%20when%20questioned%20as%20to%20how%20then%20it%20may%20obtain%20donations%20from%20publicly-funded%20institutions%2C%20it%20claims%20to%20be%20a%20public%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20Fund%20cannot%20have%20it%20both%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20citizens%20who%C2%A0%20are%C2%A0%20due%20to%20cast%C2%A0%20their%20vote%20in%20perhaps%20the%20most%20fraught%20and%20consequential%20election%20to%20parliament%20had%20better%20know%20what%20mysteries%20are%20wrapped%C2%A0%20within%20the%20electoral%20bonds%C2%A0%20enigma%20before%C2%A0%20they%20trudge%20to%20the%20polling%20booth%20with%20stars%20in%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20political%20force%20that%20has%20through%20the%20years%20made%20unrelenting%20ado%20about%20corruption%20among%20the%20political%20opposition%20has%20hardly%20any%20ground%20to%20come%20forth%20on%20the%20subject%20with%20righteous%20aplomb.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20has%20always%20claimed%20that%20its%20only%20quid%20pro%20quo%20is%20with%20the%20people%20who%20are%20last%20in%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20therefore%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20fear%20the%20unraveling%20of%20facts%20that%20pertain%20to%20corporate%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBadri%20Raina%20taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709909981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcitizens-must-know-who-pays-whom-to-cast-an-informed-vote%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20the%20top%20court%20had%20stipulated%20certain%20dates%20for%20the%20SBI%20to%20make%20the%20requisite%20disclosures%20of%20bonds%20bought%20and%20donated%2C%20it%20was%20clearly%20with%20a%20view%20to%20furnishing%20such%20information%20to%20the%20citizen%20in%20a%20given%20context.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcitizens-must-know-who-pays-whom-to-cast-an-informed-vote%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Radhika%20congratulates%20Ranveer%20in%20Gujarati%3A%20Video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709908495000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108333133%2Cimgsize-64982.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fradhika-merchant-congratulates-soon-to-be-dad-ranveer-singh-in-gujarati-on-expecting-his-first-child-with-deepika-padukone-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F108333133.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108333133.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanveer%20Singh%20and%20Deepika%20Padukone%20are%20expecting%20their%20first