l%20all%20judgments%20delivered%20by%20Justice%20Ganguly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20TMC%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20has%20accused%20Justice%20Ganguly%20of%20delivering%20judgments%20from%20a%20political%20standpoint.%20TMC%20has%20already%20indicated%20its%20intention%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20court%20to%20nullify%20all%20of%20his%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20up.%20We%20are%20the%20eligible%20candidates.%20We%20are%20qualified%20to%20become%20teachers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Aditya%2C%20another%20protester.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20his%20resignation%2C%20Justice%20Ganguly%2C%20in%20a%20media%20interview%2C%20questioned%20the%20continued%20protests%20by%20individuals%20seeking%20jobs.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20rationale%20behind%20the%20ongoing%20demonstrations.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20genuine%20chance%20of%20securing%20employment%2C%20they%20should%20have%20approached%20the%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20sitting%20judge%2C%20Justice%20Ganguly%20positioned%20himself%20as%20a%20champion%20against%20corruption.%20However%2C%20after%20announcing%20his%20intention%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbengali.abplive.com%2Fdistrict%2Fcalcutta-high-court-justice-abhijit-ganguly-says-narada-sting-operation-has-nothing-to-with-corruption-but-a-conspiracy-by-a-tmc-leader-hinting-at-abhishek-banerjee-1050826%5C%22%3E%20dismissed%20the%20Narada%20sting%20operation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20allegedly%20accepted%20money%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconspiracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuvendu%20Adhikari%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20a%20larger%20conspiracy.%20The%20Narada%20sting%20operation%20was%20orchestrated%20to%20defame%20his%20party%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Ganguly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTMC%E2%80%99s%20MLA%20in%20Kalna%2C%20Biswajit%20Kundu%2C