2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Frajkot-professor-throws-ailing-mother-off-terrace-booked-5013435%2F).%5C%22%3Ecase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20man%20confessed%20to%20throwing%20his%2064-year-old%20mother%20off%20the%20terrace%20of%20their%20home%20as%20she%20was%20ill%20and%20a%20burden.%20His%20mother%20later%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20abandonment%20and%20disregard%20for%20older%20women%20is%20all%20too%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Freferenceworkentry%2F10.1007%2F978-981-16-1914-4_13-1%5C%22%3Ecommon%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20a%20country%20like%20India%20where%20filial%20piety%20is%20upheld%20as%20a%20virtue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAge%20compounds%20the%20hardships%20of%20many%20older%20women%20in%20a%20society%20marked%20by%20gender%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlder%20women%20face%20additional%20challenges%20of%20financial%20insecurity%2C%20destitution%20and%20health%20challenges%20related%20to%20ageing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20neoliberal%20society%2C%20people%20are%20valued%20for%20their%20economic%20contribution.%20A%20similar%20logic%20operates%20in%20many%20Indian%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20older%20family%20member%20is%20not%20earning%20an%20income%2C%20they%20are%20deemed%20to%20be%20dependents%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98burden%E2%80%99.%20Patriarchal%20cultural%20norms%20relegate%20women%20to%20domestic%20duties.%20Many%20women%20remain%20unemployed%20throughout%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20a%20majority%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.helpageindia.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2FWomen-Ageing-Invisible-or-Empowered-a-HelpAge-India-2023-report.pdf%5C%22%3Edo%20not%20own%20assets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20creates%20economic%20hardships%20in%20late%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202015%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.agewellfoundation.org%2Fpdf%2Freports%2FGENDER%2520DISCRIMINATION%2520AMONG%2520OLDER%2520WOMEN%2520IN%2520INDIA.pdf%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20older%20women%20have%20a%20diminished%20status%20in%20the%20family%20because%20they%20do%20not%20earn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F13600810601045833%3Ftab%3Dpermissions%26scroll%3Dtop%5C%22%3Eeven%20though%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20contribute%20to%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20families%20by%20being%20caregivers%20for%20grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20care%20work%20in%20the%20family%20remains%20highly%20devalued.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.unfpa.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpub-pdf%2F20230926_india_ageing_report_2023_web_version_.pdf)%5C%22%3Efeminisation%20of%20ageing%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20increased%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F43473%5C%22%3Elife%20expectancy%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20women%20(compared%20to%20men)%20implies%20that%20older%20women%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20dependent%20on%20others%20for%20prolonged%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20dependent%20on%20kin%20can%20exacerbate%20vulnerabilities.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1007%2F978-981-10-3439-8_3%5C%22%3Eresearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Eshows%20that%20older%20women%20could%20be%20easy%20targets%20of%20coercion%20and%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20propertied%20older%20women%2C%20many%20experience%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmaharashtra%2Fmany-elderly-not-being-looked-after-withering-joint-family-system-to-blamemumbai-high-court-2870735%5C%22%3Eabuse%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20transferring%20property%20to%20their%20adult%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20women%20in%20the%20country%20do%20not%20own%20property%20despite%20there%20being%20laws%20which%20grant%20property%20rights%20to%20women.%20Such%20women%20are%20sometimes%20driven%20to%20destitution%2C%20and%20many%20are%20abandoned%20by%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlder%20women%20can%20claim%20maintenance%20from%20family%20members%20under%20existing%20legal%20provisions%20in%20India.%20Section%2019%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F1638%2F1%2FAA1956____78.pdf%5C%22%3EHindu%20Adoptions%20and%20Maintenance%20Act%2C%201956%3C%2Fa%3E%20allows%20a%20widow%20(who%20does%20not%20remarry)%20to%20claim%20maintenance%20from%20the%20legal%20heirs%20of%20the%20deceased%20who%20share%20the%20property%20of%20the%20deceased.%20Widows%20can%20also%20claim%20maintenance%20under%20Section%20125%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20from%20their%20children%2C%20unconditionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F6831%2F1%2Fmaintenance_and_welfare_of_parents_and_senior_citizens_act.pdf%5C%22%3EThe%20Maintenance%20and%20Welfare%20of%20Parents%20and%20Senior%20Citizens%20Act%2C%202007%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20MW%20Act%2C%20was%20formulated%20especially%20for%20senior%20citizens%E2%80%99%20welfare.%20Section%204%20obligates%20sons%2C%20daughters%2C%20grandchildren%20who%20are%20not%20minors%20and%20any%20legal%20heir%20of%20her%20property%20to%20provide%20maintenance.%20This%20law%20defines%20maintenance%20as%20food%2C%20clothing%2C%20shelter%20and%20medical%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20safeguards%20against%20abandonment%2C%20usurpation%20of%20property%20and%20abuse%20exist%20in%20the%20MW%20Act%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fhandle%2F123456789%2F2021%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAn%2520Act%2520to%2520provide%2520for%2Cconnected%2520therewith%2520or%2520incidental%2520thereto.%26amp%3Btext%3DNotification%253A%2CS.O.%5C%22%3EProtection%20of%20Women%20from%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act%2C%202005%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20existing%20laws%2C%20however%2C%20do%20not%20particularly%20address%20the%20discrimination%20faced%20by%20some%20older%20women%20such%20as%20childless%2C%20unmarried%20or%20trans%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2FBillsTexts%2FLSBillTexts%2FAsintroduced%2F161%2520OF%25202022%2520AS.pdf%3Fsource%3Dlegislation%5C%22%3EProtection%20of%20Rights%20of%20Widows%20and%20Single%20Women%20and%20Abolishment%20of%20Widowhood%20Practices%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20introduced%20in%202022%20but%20nothing%20came%20of%20it.%20Destigmatising%20widowhood%20and%20singlehood%20and%20restoring%20dignity%20to%20those%20belonging%20to%20sexual%20minorities%20is%20crucial%20for%20empowering%20older%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20laws%20undoubtedly%20safeguard%20the%20rights%20of%20older%20women%2C%20it%20is%20impractical%20to%20conjure%20a%20law%20for%20every%20situation%20of%20harm%20done%20to%20older%20women%3B%20rather%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20proactively%20implement%20existing%20laws.%20As%20political%20theorist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1111%2F1467-8675.00183%5C%22%3EWendy%20Brown%3C%2Fa%3E%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%98%E2%80%A6rights%E2%80%A6serve%20as%20a%20mitigation%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20a%20resolution%20%E2%80%94%20of%20subordinating%20powers.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatriarchal%20ideas%20that%20prevent%20women%20from%20pursuing%20a%20life%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20choice%20must%20be%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20women%20remain%20engaged%20in%20care%20work%20throughout%20their%20lives.%20A%20woman%20at%20a%20charitable%20care%20home%20in%20Kolkata%20said%20%E2%80%98she%20found%20herself%E2%80%99%20after%20relocating%20to%20the%20care%20home%20after%20her%20spouse%E2%80%99s%20death.%20She%20was%20relieved%20of%20the%20care%20work%20and%20now%20she%20was%20%E2%80%98free.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECare%20work%20must%20be%20accorded%20due%20importance%20in%20the%20political%20discourse.%20Restoring%20dignity%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20and%20building%20a%20supportive%20environment%20for%20women%20to%20perform%20their%20caring%20duties%20often%20determines%20their%20wellbeing%20in%20late%20life.%20Many%20women%20combat%20loneliness.%20More%20recreation%20facilities%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20can%20be%20made%20available.%20Age-appropriate%20occupations%20can%20be%20considered%20for%20women%20to%20enhance%20financial%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsuring%20safety%2C%20access%20to%20helplines%20and%20counselling%20support%2C%20access%20to%20inexpensive%20medical%20care%2C%20palliative%20care%2C%20dementia%20care%2C%20affordable%20permanent%20housing%2C%20and%20financial%20security%20through%20pension%20schemes%20are%20areas%20where%20attention%20needs%20to%20be%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20concern%20of%20many%20older%20women%20living%20in%20cities%2C%20as%20per%20my%20research%2C%20has%20been%20sourcing%20essentials%20and%20recruiting%20reliable%20care%20workers%20for%20themselves.%20Crimes%20against%20older%20women%20in%20cities%20such%20as%20murder%2C%20robbery%20and%20assault%20are%20often%20reported%20especially%20in%20metropolitan%20cities%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20older%20women%20interviewed%20mentioned%20how%20they%20would%20prefer%20shifting%20to%20institutional%20care%20rather%20than%20relying%20on%20paid%20domestic%20workers%20and%20%3Ci%3Eayahs%3C%2Fi%3E.%20This%20also%20highlights%20the%20need%20to%20have%20more%20care%20homes%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%2C%20community%2C%20as%20well%20as%20regulated%20market%20intervention%20in%20the%20above%20domains%2C%20is%20key%20to%20providing%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20older%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Older%20women%E2%80%99%20is%20not%20a%20homogenous%20category.%20Therefore%2C%20identifying%20unique%20needs%20based%20on%20their%20context%20is%20also%20crucial%20to%20meet%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.who.int%2Fmedia%2Fdocs%2Fdefault-source%2Fdecade-of-healthy-ageing%2Fdecade-proposal-final-apr2020-en.pdf%5C%22%3EUN%20Decade%20of%20Healthy%20Ageing%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2021-2030).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDr.%20Deblina%20Dey%20is%20Associate%20Professor%20of%20Sociology%20%26amp%3B%20Assistant%20Director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Humanities%20at%20the%20Law%20School%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20She%20is%20pursuing%20her%20postdoctoral%20research%20on%20care%20interventions%20for%20older%20people%20in%20urban%20India.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EOriginally%20published%20under%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ECreative%20Commons%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F360info.org%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E360info%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%84%A2.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709902815000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08173620%2Fimage-1924.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fabused-abandoned-neglected-the-plight-of-indias-older-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Restoring%20dignity%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20can%20give%20older%20women%20the%20care%20and%20respect%20they%20deserve%20in%20late%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fabused-abandoned-neglected-the-plight-of-indias-older-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22To%20the%20PM%2C%20From%20Kaziranga%3A%20An%20Open%20Letter%20Decrying%20Displacement%2C%20Human%20Rights%20Violations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F08122740%2FDAvKGMrV0AEbHas.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Assam%20with%20his%20arrival%20at%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20scheduled%20for%20March%208.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDear%20Mr.%20Prime%20Minister%2C%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHope%20you%20are%20doing%20fine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%2C%20the%20people%20living%20near%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20and%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20would%20like%20to%20send%20you%20our%20respect%20and%20greetings.%20We%20take%20great%20pride%20in%20our%20role%20as%20the%20wardens%20of%20this%20land%20since%20time%20immemorial%20%E2%80%93%20long%20before%20kingdoms%2C%20empires%2C%20states%2C%20and%20governments%20were%20formed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20we%20still%20continue%20to%20take%20utmost%20care%20of%20our%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYour%20coming%20has%20ushered%20in%20a%20sense%20of%20great%20festivity%20as%20we%20see%20hundreds%20of%20armed%20police%20personnel%20moving%20around%20the%20area.%20It%20feels%20like%20we%20are%20in%20an%20Orwellian%20act.%20Would%20that%20be%20the%20norm%20for%20our%20future%3F%20They%20are%20frisking%20people%20and%20putting%20up%20roadblocks%20and%20barricades%20in%20many%20places.%20It%20seems%20%3Cspan%3Elike%3C%2Fspan%3E%20it%20is%20becoming%20a%20norm%20as%20we%20see%20different%20flag%20marches%20by%20police%20and%20commandos%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20television%20channels%20air%20them%20with%20much%20pride%20and%20pomp%20as%20if%20it%20is%20something%20good.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20wonder%20why%20not%20much%20of%20the%20camera%20goes%20to%20the%20other%20side%20where%20people%20could%20express%20their%20anguish%20of%20forceful%20displacement%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fstatic%2Fkaziranga-rhino-poaching%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20human%20rights%20violations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20also%20take%20place%20in%20Kaziranga.%20However%2C%20we%20keep%20hearing%20that%20in%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20everything%20is%20rosy%20and%20bright.%20Perhaps%20we%20have%20no%20idea%20of%20what%20it%20is%20as%20we%20rarely%20see%20much%20of%20what%20the%20developed%20and%20rich%20world%20looks%20like.%20We%20are%20happy%20that%20if%20you%20take%20a%20keen%20look%2C%20you%20will%20see%20what%20rich%20land%20with%20poor%20people%20looks%20like%20due%20to%20lopsided%20development%20for%20a%20few.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20chief%20minister%2C%20Dr.%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20seemed%20exuberant%20about%20your%20visit.%20He%20has%20taken%20the%20onus%20of%20saying%20out%20loud%20that%20his%20government%20has%20brought%20a%20prime%20minister%20to%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20the%20biodiversity.%20Hopefully%2C%20the%20golden%20tiger%2C%20that%20our%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20boasting%20about%2C%20will%20give%20a%20sighting%20to%20our%20royal%20guest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20rumour%20that%20you%20would%20be%20staying%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvaanigreens.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVaani%20Greens%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20place%20specially%20curated%20by%20our%20honourable%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20family.%20We%20are%20often%20enticed%20by%20the%20beautiful%20pictures%20that%20come%20out%20of%20the%20sprawling%20tea%20garden%20and%20the%20cottages%20that%20look%20like%20igloos%2C%20set%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20an%20animal%20corridor.%20The%20media%20also%20keeps%20saying%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthecrosscurrent.in%2Fkanchanjuri_03_03_2023%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%E2%80%99s%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Kanchanjuri%20Animal%20Corridor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20the%20powerful%20to%20decide%2C%20who%20are%20we%3F%20Oh%2C%20the%20irony%20of%20our%20times%2C%20people%20are%20gossip-mongers%20and%20we%20know%20that%20you%20would%20be%20staying%20in%20a%20government%20property%20in%20Kohora%20%E2%80%93%20the%20epicentre%20of%20tourism%20in%20Kaziranga.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERespected%20prime%20minister%2C%20we%20wish%20you%20could%20stay%20in%20the%20Grand%20Hyatt%20hotel%2C%20which%20is%20being%20built%20on%20Adivasi%2Ftea%20tribe%20land%20without%20any%20form%20of%20consultation%20or%20compensation.%20We%20are%20also%20confused%20about%20how%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20with%20120%20rooms%20can%20be%20built%20on%20farmlands%20which%20were%20also%20used%20by%20elephants%20as%20their%20corridor.%20We%20are%20concerned%20about%20what%20is%20happening%20behind%20your%20back.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20accomplice%2C%20the%20health%20minister%20of%20Assam%2C%20share%20boundaries%20of%20their%20huge%20gated%20and%20fenced%20properties%20in%20Kaziranga%2C%20but%20we%2C%20the%20poor%20and%20unwanted%2C%20are%20finding%20it%20difficult%20to%20protect%20our%20legal%20rights%20to%20the%20little%20lands%20that%20we%20cultivate%20to%20feed%20ourselves%20and%20the%20wild%20animals%20of%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20and%20Tiger%20Reserve.%20This%20is%20not%20fair%2C%20what%20they%20are%20doing%20to%20you%20%E2%80%93%20who%20claims%20with%20such%20pride%20that%20there%20will%20be%20zero%20tolerance%20against%20illegalities%20and%20also%20the%20famous%20phrases%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENa%20khaunga%2C%20na%20khaane%20doonga%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9CSab%20ka%20saath%20sab%20ka%20vikas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20tourism%20minister%2C%20Jayanta%20Malla%20Baruah%2C%20has%20talked%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20your%20visit%20which%20would%20help%20Kaziranga%20in%20its%20promotion.%20We%20wonder%20what%20more%20could%20come%20up%20into%20the%20UNESCO%20site.%20Kaziranga%20has%20seen%20every%20inch%20of%20farm%20and%20fallow%20land%20being%20gradually%20swallowed%20by%20big%20hotel%20chains%20like%20the%20Grand%20Hyatt%2C%20Taj%20Hotels%2C%20Vaani%20Greens%2C%20IORA%2C%20Borgos%2C%20Mandu%2C%20Royal%20de%20Casa%2C%20etc.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20people%20complaining%20about%20how%20the%20farmlands%20are%20being%20changed%20into%20commercial%20plots%20overnight%2C%20though%20there%20is%20a%20strict%20forest%20department%20and%20revenue%20office%20which%20are%20supposed%20to%20safeguard%20the%20land.%20And%20how%20hills%20have%20been%20flattened%20and%20walls%20built%2C%20that%20have%20killed%20perennial%20streams%20and%20lakes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOh%20dear%20prime%20minister%2C%20we%20would%20want%20you%20to%20come%20and%20sit%20in%20a%20mud%20or%20a%20bamboo%20stilt%20house%20in%20some%20village%20like%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F977999%2Fas-kaziranga-national-park-spreads-local-residents-tear-down-their-homes-before-they-are-evicted%2523%3A~%3Atext%3DEvictions%252520in%252520Kaziranga%252520usually%252520attract%2Cvoluntarily%2525E2%252580%25259D%252520tore%252520down%252520their%252520homes.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Hatikhuli%20Borbil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Its%20residents%20have%20been%20living%20there%20for%20generations%20and%20suddenly%2C%20one%20fine%20day%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20their%20land.%20Now%20they%20are%20facing%20eviction%20without%20any%20form%20of%20rehabilitation.%20Does%20that%20sound%20fair%20to%20you%3F%20You%2C%20as%20a%20universal%20leader%2C%20surely%20know%20that%20indigenous%20communities%20are%20the%20best%20wardens%20of%20the%20land%20and%20forest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPardon%20us%2C%20apart%20from%20our%20uncertain%20future%2C%20we%20would%20want%20to%20feed%20you%20with%20the%20best%20foraged%20vegetables%2C%20Namsing%20(fermented%20fish)%2C%20Apong%2FHariya%20(used%20for%20rituals)%2C%20fermented%20drinks%20that%20keep%20our%20ancestors%20and%20us%20happy%20and%20connected%2C%20and%20show%20you%20our%20ecologically%20sensible%20and%20frugal%20living.%20We%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20have%20you%2C%20the%20way%20you%20have%20done%20before%20every%20election%2C%20visiting%20some%20Dalit%20households%20in%20mainland%20India.%20Our%20poor%20evicted%20villagers%20of%20Kaziranga%20would%20also%20take%20great%20pride%20if%20you%20would%20come%20to%20sit%20in%20our%20humble%20dwellings%20squatting%20over%20roads%20and%20embankments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20hope%20your%20security%20is%20tight%20enough%20as%20we%20see%20barricades%20and%20flag%20marches%20too.%20We%20are%20well-surveilled%2C%20too%2C%20with%20the%20patrolling%20commandos%20and%20special%20task%20forces%20who%20spend%20all%20their%20time%20in%20the%20civilian%20areas%20rather%20than%20the%20forest%20areas.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20ask%20how%20our%20villagers%20are%20scared%20to%20even%20venture%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20as%20there%20have%20been%20so%20many%20incidents%20where%20they%20have%20been%20thrashed%20by%20those%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fkaziranga-bbc-shoot-poaching%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egun-wielding%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20forest%20guards%20under%20mere%20suspicion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOh%2C%20did%20you%20know%2C%20the%20forest%20guards%20here%20enjoy%20great%20powers%20to%20use%20their%20guns%20which%20they%20say%20can%20shoot%20at%20the%20sight%20of%20anyone%20inside%20the%20park%20boundaries%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20if%20we%20poor%20people%20knew%20the%20boundaries%2C%20as%20Kaziranga%20started%20with%20around%20300%20sq%20km%20area%20and%20today%20it%20boasts%20of%20more%20than%201%2C100%20km%20territory%2C%20so%20tell%20us%20whose%20mathematics%20is%20going%20wrong.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20understand%20the%20presence%20of%20so%20many%20police%20and%20military%20when%20you%20are%20here%2C%20but%20why%20does%20Kaziranga%20have%20such%20high%20security%20in%20civilian%20areas%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20and%20it%20is%20only%20increasing.%20Some%20people%20say%20it%20is%20a%20colonial%20hangover%20as%20the%20forest%20department%20is%20one%20institution%20that%20has%20not%20changed%20much%20since.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20so%20much%20that%20we%20would%20like%20to%20share%20but%20only%20if%20there%20was%20time%20for%20you%20to%20listen%20to%20our%20elders%20about%20the%20unbroken%20history%20of%20broken%20promises.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20bid%20you%20farewell%2C%20let%20history%20judge%20itself%2C%20while%20we%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20survive%2C%20maintain%20sanity%20and%20dignity%2C%20and%20bring%20in%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWarm%20regards%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPranab%20Doley%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPranab%20Doley%20is%20a%20youth%20leader%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20community%20of%20Bokakhat%20displaced%20by%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709901051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F08122740%2FDAvKGMrV0AEbHas.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fto-the-pm-from-kaziranga-an-open-letter-decrying-displacement-human-rights-violations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Assam%20with%20his%20arrival%20at%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20scheduled%20for%20March%208.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fto-the-pm-from-kaziranga-an-open-letter-decrying-displacement-human-rights-violations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Would%20a%20temporary%20dock%20help%20get%20aid%20into%20Gaza%3F%20Here's%20how%20it%20could%20work%2