.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20not%20been%20a%20single%20day%20when%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20hot%20food.%20Priya%20makes%20sure%20that%20this%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20affect%20household%20duties.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20would%20worry%20about%20how%20they%E2%80%99ll%20fend%20for%20themselves%20when%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20savings.%20But%20today%2C%20I%20take%20pride%20that%20Priya%20has%20earned%20financial%20freedom%20as%20well%20as%20popularity.%20She%20is%20so%20enthusiastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20house%20helps%20have%20aspirations%20beyond%20our%20kitchen%20and%20homes.%20If%20we%20just%20recognise%20them%20and%20give%20them%20that%20little%20push%2C%20then%20the%20sky%20is%20the%20limit.%20We%20just%20need%20to%20act%20as%20a%20small%20catalyst%20in%20helping%20such%20women%20achieve%20their%20aspirations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Priya%20says%20she%20has%20not%20only%20learnt%20to%20set%20up%20the%20small%20business%20but%20also%20to%20ensure%20a%20sustainable%20financial%20future%20for%20her%20family.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20get%20big%20profits%2C%20I%20deposit%20all%20my%20money.%20With%20this%20work%2C%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20establish%20an%20identity%20for%20myself.%20I%20also%20got%20a%20kitchen%20refurbished%20in%20our%20village%20home%20and%20bought%20a%20double%20bed%20for%20my%20home%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAbhi%20tension%20nahi%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20anything%20now).%20We%20do%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20how%20much%20we%20are%20spending%20on%20our%20village%20home%20and%20how%20much%20we%20are%20able%20to%20save%20to%20secure%20our%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20her%20transformation%20from%20the%20old%20days%2C%20Priya%20wishes%20to%20encourage%20other%20women%20like%20her.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20I%20earlier%20and%20what%20am%20I%20now!%20I%20believe%20other%20women%20can%20also%20start%20small%20businesses%20for%20additional%20income%20sources.%20It%20is%20all%20about%20your%20hard%20work%20and%20the%20community%20support%20with%20which%20you%20can%20achieve%20financial%20freedom%20like%20I%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20reside%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20you%20can%20join%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FonR5s7uTaMe5w6P37%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%20group%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20place%20orders%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FonR5s7uTaMe5w6P37%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fwomens-day-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Farticle-image-1709897002.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%23HelpThemBack%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Farticle-image-1709897002.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Farticle-image-1709897002-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Farticle-image-1709897002-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Farticle-image-1709897002-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Farticle-image-1709897002-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344354%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Prani