epeated%20the%20whole%20process.%20This%20time%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20successfully%20dry%20and%20powder%20the%20flowers.%20Using%20these%20powdered%20flowers%2C%20ghee%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98havan%E2%80%99%20products%2C%20and%20other%20ingredients%2C%20she%20tried%20her%20hand%20at%20making%20dhoop%20sticks.%20Through%20some%20permutations%20and%20combinations%2C%20and%20hours%20of%20working%2C%20she%20found%20the%20winning%20combination%20of%2016%20herbs%20sometime%20in%20September%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20Janmashtami%202019.%20I%20took%20these%20dhoop%20sticks%20and%20gave%20them%20to%20the%20temple%20priest%20who%20supported%20me.%20He%20was%20so%20happy%20and%20promised%20to%20give%20me%20segregated%20floral%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20entrepreneur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20initially%20invested%20her%20savings%20into%20the%20business%2C%20Poonam%20also%20took%20a%20Mudra%20loan%20to%20support%20her%20venture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claims%20that%20her%20products%20are%20organic%20and%20made%20with%20almost%2080%20percent%20floral%20waste.%20Unlike%20other%20incense%20and%20dhoop%20sticks%2C%20Aaruhi%20products%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20charcoal%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%203%2C000%20%E2%80%98Flower%20Recyclers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201242px)%20100vw%2C%201242px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poonam%20has%20trained%20over%203000%20women%20in%20flower%20recycling%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365.jpeg%201242w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365-300x296.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett