kthrough%20by%20turning%20agri-waste%20into%20high-value%20nanocarbon%20for%20use%20in%20batteries.%20That%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20our%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Akshay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahi%20points%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20people%20are%20adopting%20EVs%2C%20alongside%20a%20growing%20interest%20in%20adopting%20renewable%20solar%20energy%2C%20both%20of%20which%20rely%20on%20batteries.%20By%20speaking%20to%20various%20people%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20existing%20batteries%2C%20which%20are%20made%20with%20carbons%20derived%20from%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20face%20challenges%20related%20to%20lifespan%2C%20charging%2C%20warranty%20returns%2C%20and%20safety.%20We%20saw%20this%20as%20a%20huge%20plug-in%20for%20our%20innovation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20and%20Mahi%20decided%20to%20marry%20both%20concerns%20of%20growing%20agricultural%20waste%20and%20rising%20demand%20for%20batteries%2C%20and%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20the%20same%20stone!%20In%202020%2C%20Akshay%20and%20Mahi%20launched%20their%20startup%20%E2%80%98Cancrie%E2%80%99%20to%20commercialise%20their%20patented%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FCancrie-2-1709646778.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20claims%20their%20nanocarbon%20increases%20battery%20performance%20and%20reduces%20the%20need%20for%20raw%20material%20extraction%20for%20battery%20production.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FCancrie-2-1709646778.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FCancrie-2-1709646778-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FCancrie-2-1709646778-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co