2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20stories%20hold%20personal%20meaning%20for%20Kathait%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20Dehradun%20near%20a%20famed%20tiger%20reserve.%20He%20would%20often%20hear%20heart-wrenching%20stories%20of%20locals%20being%20mauled%20to%20death.%20Being%20able%20to%20now%20be%20a%20part%20of%20a%20smart%20solution%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20him.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20protecting%20humans%2C%20but%20also%20wildlife%2C%20he%20emphasises.%20As%20a%20testament%20to%20Valiance%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20using%20AI%20for%20social%20good%2C%20the%20Wildlife%20Eye%20is%20community-centric%20in%20that%20it%20prioritises%20local%20community%20benefits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20Kathait%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20value%20of%20human%20life%20is%20immeasurable%2C%20and%20assigning%20a%20numerical%20figure%20to%20it%20is%20beyond%20consideration.%20The%20loss%20of%20human%20lives%20or%20livestock%20in%20animal%20attacks%20not%20only%20bears%20a%20substantial%20financial%20burden%20on%20the%20exchequer%20running%20into%20crores%2C%20but%20it%20also%20creates%20social%20unrest.%20Our%20solution%20endeavours%20to%20avert%20such%20incidents%2C%20thereby%20enhancing%20overall%20safety%20and%20mitigating%20the%20economic%20and%20emotional%20toll%20associated%20with%20these%20unfortunate%20events.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20model%20has%20experienced%20success%2C%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20without%20its%20challenges.%20The%20lack%20of%20a%20robust%20network%20in%20the%20villages%20of%20Chandrapur%20posed%20a%20hindrance%20in%20transmitting%20images%20to%20the%20algorithm.%20To%20overcome%20this%20issue%2C%20Kathait%20and%20his%20team%20had%20to%20develop%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277445%2Fdelhi-brothers-rescue-injured-birds-kite-flying-wildlife-clinic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20technical%20breakthrough%3C%2