they%20helped%20me%20enrol%20in%20a%20government%20school.%20After%20completing%20class%2010%2C%20when%20I%20went%20back%20to%20my%20hometown%2C%20I%20was%20informed%20that%20my%20marriage%20had%20been%20fixed%20with%20a%20man%20who%20was%2010%20years%20older%20than%20me.%20At%20my%20%3Cem%3Ehaldi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eceremony%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20team%20from%20the%20NGO%20came%20to%20my%20rescue%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20police%2C%20my%20marriage%20was%20stopped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20Pune%20and%20continued%20my%20higher%20studies%20till%20class%2012%20and%20secured%20a%20job%20in%20a%20bank.%20Whatever%20I%20am%20today%20is%20because%20of%20the%20efforts%20of%20this%20NGO%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20long-term%20impact%20post-handholding%2C%20Manjusha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20we%20organised%20an%20alumni%20meet%20of%20our%20200%20students.%20It%20was%20really%20overwhelming%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20how%20these%20children%20are%20doing%20well%20in%20their%20lives.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20working%20with%20multinational%20companies%2C%20some%20of%20them%20have%20become%20principals%20of%20schools%2C%20and%20some%20are%20working%20at%20the%20construction%20site%2C%20but%20as%20civil%20engineers%20and%20not%20as%20labourers.%20The%20impact%20motivates%20us%20to%20keep%20on%20going.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Manjusha%20Doshi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709218222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FTMCP-1709217275.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20a%20belief%20that%20every%20child%20has%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20education%2C%20health%20care%2C%20and%20a%20secure%20future%2C%20Tara%20Mobile%20Creches%20Pune%20has%20been%20working%20for%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20children%20of%20migrant%20families.%20With%20its%20mobile%20cr%C3%A8ches%2C%20it%20has%20catered%20to%201%20lakh%20such%20kids.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343596%2Fdaycare-in-pune-for-migrant-kids-tara-mobile-creches-pune-jobs-for-kids-of-migrant-workers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coronavirus%3A%202nd%20Person%20Dies%20In%20U.S.%3B%20New%20Cases%20Reported%20In%20Florida%20And%20New%20York%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20second%20person%20has%20died%20from%20COVID-19%20in%20the%20U.S.%2C%20officials%20in%20Washington%20state%20say.%20With%20new%20coronavirus%20cases%20being%20reported%20in%20several%20states%2C%20a%20woman%20wears%20a%20medical%20mask%20during%20a%20campaign%20rally%20for%20Sen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%20in%20California.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.npr.org%2Fassets%2Fimg%2F2020%2F03%2F02%2Fcoronavirus-ca-ny-florida_wide-99e88ad3179d6418e830fead4d0e3cc889543149.jpg%3Fs%3D600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20was%20in%20his%2070s%20and%20had%20been%20living%20at%20a%20nursing%20facility%20near%20Seattle%20that's%20now%20suspected%20of%20being%20the%20site%20of%20America's%20first%20outbreak%20of%20the%20novel%20coronavirus.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Image%20credit%3A%20David%20McNew%2FGetty%20Images)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.npr.org%2Finclude%2Fimages%2Ftracking%2Fnpr-rss-pixel.png%3Fstory%3D811161998%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1583157474000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.npr.org%2Fassets%2Fimg%2F2020%2F03%2F02%2Fcoronavirus-ca-ny-florida_wide-99e88ad3179d6418e830fead4d0e3cc889543149.jpg%3Fs%3D600%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Fhealth-shots%2F2020%2F03%2F02%2F811161998%2Fcoronavirus-2nd-person-dies-in-u-s-new-cases-reported-in-florida-and-new-york%3Futm_medium%3DRSS%26